**OrderItem Table:**
| Field          | Type        | Constraints              | Description           |
|----------------|-------------|--------------------------|-----------------------|
| item_id        | int         | PRIMARY KEY              | Item ID               |
| order_id       | int         | NOT NULL                 | Order ID              |
| product_id     | int         | NOT NULL                 | Product ID            |
| unit_price     | float       | NOT NULL                 | Unit price            |
| quantity       | int         | NOT NULL                 | Quantity ordered      |
| discount_rate  | float       |                          | Discount percentage   |
| tax_rate       | float       |                          | Tax percentage        |

